title: Met Gala 2021: Get Ready with Me | Hailey Rhode Bieber
author: Hailey Rhode Bieber
description:
I’m so excited to be back at the Met Gala this year! It was Justin and I’s first time attending together, and it was also our three-year anniversary which made the night extra special. I wanted to give you all a behind-the-scenes look into the process of getting ready - check it out!
